# Student Record Management System (C++)

## Overview
This is a console-based Student Record Management System developed using C++. The project helps in managing student data efficiently such as adding, searching, deleting, displaying, and restoring records.

---

## Features
- Add new student details (Name, ID, Course, Marks)
- Search student by ID
- Search student by Marks
- Display all student records
- Delete student record (normal method)
- Stack-based delete with undo (restore feature)
- Restore previously deleted student record

---

## Technologies Used
- C++
- Arrays
- Object-Oriented Programming (OOP concepts)
- Stack-like structure (for undo functionality)

---

## How to Run
1. Download the source code
2. Open it in any C++ compiler (VS Code / CodeBlocks / Dev C++)
3. Compile the program
4. Run the executable file
5. Follow the on-screen instructions

---

